{"tid":1758264,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想唔想幫香港? 做一件小事就得","createTime":"2019-11-27T02:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T06:08:11.000Z","uid":211848,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db9459117c781ac380f5749e941cf66cb49016ba","tid":1758264,"uid":211848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"大家係屋企寫定一張memo 出街, 落街經過連儂牆就痴<br />\n<br />\n好對唔住, 做左標題黨 (因為聽講咁樣可以引到人入黎) <br />\n但真心既<br />\n各區連儂牆真係好需要大家,而且呢件事好簡單<br />\n<br />\n對家清既速度太快<br />\n文宣隊痴既速度唔夠快, 所以更加需要大家既力量, 重新加固連儂牆, <br />\n一黎可以加士氣<br />\n二黎對方會清到攰 <br />\n三黎文宣隊更容易更新連儂牆 (愈多人cover , 對家落手前都要諗諗)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有另一件更易既事可以做<br />\n就係幫我推post, 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c2e5426f1aa43dc720c978b1761f441aa84074","tid":1758264,"uid":211848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:50:12.000Z","msg":"推下啦"},{"pid":"363c2269fdd9210126a354c87c25730a27e442b1","tid":1758264,"uid":211848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d44957aae672108a74a690340794467c035298a","tid":1758264,"uid":211848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1639a8433e62c05e7252a10d77666166bd8797c","tid":1758264,"uid":211848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"行動post黎架,<br />\n幫幫手"},{"pid":"ec4f80d81d5005e339477c6c43e810191e006661","tid":1758264,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"38d0513c1b5629a9581b43c1666fc1803c5509dc","tid":1758264,"uid":119534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b61c0399fc6ab6843968957ea324d99cacff058d","tid":1758264,"uid":211848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"df8ba4be2492f67812394a0b9f335e1a08a28ea3","tid":1758264,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"!"},{"pid":"aeca5bfcdabb47674933ca392d4e98756d27de40","tid":1758264,"uid":211848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48b2c6d16b813844fbad2fa4de5d66654b29747","tid":1758264,"uid":211848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41f69d9de6b3953c243c2735e3a5d5f6ec8f529d","tid":1758264,"uid":6152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:08:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}